data.description:
Beautiful one level brick 1/2 block off
19-E. Panoramic mountain views. 3 Br, 2 Full baths, Large open floor plan . Great laundry room with office. Large handicapped master suite with
plenty of privcy  walk in shower and closet. Both additional BR'S have double closets, ceiling fans throughout. Lots of updates including, new waterproof laminate flooring throughout, new stainless appliances, new water heater, new interior doors, new window blinds.
Large double attached garage with coated Team Red concrete floor. Covered front porch with mountain views. Large back deck with mountain view. Large above ground pool with utility shed and new robot vacuum system. 22 X 30 detached garage with workshop. Extra utility building. 300 Gallon Propane tank included.This property has it all and is within 1/2 block off 19-E and 10 minutes to downtown Elizabethton. Pristine one level home.Great neighborhood within walking distance to Hampton High School.  Property is in a flood plain, has never been flooded. Seller Motivated . Call Showing Time for appt.
